FBIS4-29915 "dreas120_c_94029" FBIS-EAS-94-120 Daily Report 18 Jun 1994 North Korea Belgian Labor Party Chairman Arrives 18 Jun Belgian Labor Party Chairman Arrives 18 Jun SK1806233794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 2213 GMT 18 Jun 94 SK1806233794 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 18 (KCNA) -- Tudo Martens, chairman of the Central Committee of the Belgian Labour Party, and his entourage arrived here today. They were met at the airport by Hwang Chang-yop secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea.
